    section#main-section.top-section
        .top-section-wrapper
            .top-section-inner
                .container
                    .image-content.col-md-6
                        img(src="/img/ultimo-theme.png", alt="Ultimo Theme")
                    .text-content.col-md-6
                        h1.hero-caption
                            | The Unified
